BRAND NEW CONSTRUCTION_PREMIUM UPGRADES: **End Unit, only 1 neighbor** ATTACHED GARAGED**_KITCHEN AID APPLIANCES **Whirpool 4-Door Flex French Door Smart Refrigerator in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel**_Wrought Iron Stair rail 
Granite Counter tops_Barn House Sink_**PREMIUM Glass Shower Enclosures, NOT Aluminum shower enclosures **Upgraded Ceiling Fans in every room & Pendant Lighting in the Kitchen and GRAND Decorative Lighting Fixture in the Entry Way Welcome to the premier Gated community of Isles of Lake Nona, where Luxury and convenience come together in this modern townhome. As you step into the home, the open foyer leads you to a Private bedroom and a full bath, providing flexibility and privacy for guests or family members. The first level of the home is designed for entertaining and exceeds expectations. The well-appointed kitchen overlooks the spacious living room and dining area, creating a seamless flow for everyday living. Adorned with Designer finishes, including upgraded 42" custom cabinets, gorgeous GRANITE countertops, Stainless Steel appliances, and a large breakfast bar, the kitchen is a perfect blend of style and functionality. Upstairs, you'll discover a serene retreat in the oversized primary suite. Bathed in natural light, this impressive space features a well-appointed Ensuite with dual sinks, a spacious Glass shower, walk-in closet. Two additional spacious bedrooms and another full bathroom are thoughtfully positioned off the hallway, providing comfort and convenience for the whole family. The laundry room is also conveniently located upstairs, making laundry day a breeze. Step outside through the living room and find a peaceful outdoor retreat in the Courtyard, accessible through a covered walkway that leads to the detached two-car rear garage adding practicality and convenience to your daily routine. Isles of Lake Nona is a Gated, Resort-Style, Waterfront community that caters to its residents' needs. Resort-Style Pool with a Splash pad, socialize in the community room, stay active in the Fitness center, or enjoy the Playgrounds, Tennis courts, and Basketball courts. This Exceptional community is conveniently located just minutes away from shopping and dining, the vibrant Lake Nona Town Center, and the Prestigious Lake Nona Medical City area and Laureate Park. With easy access to the 417, commuting to Downtown, Disney, or either Coast has never been easier! Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhome your dream home at Isles of Lake Nona. Schedule a tour today and discover the Waterfront lifestyle and unparalleled Amenities that await you in this Exceptional community.
